memo:
There is no 0.1uf capacitor on list of Elecrow Parts Library.
If you have any stock of 0603 size 0.1nf capacitor, please use that.

Footprint is pinheader(male) but expected component is pinsocket(female)
Cut the component to 17 pins or use similar one it has around 10mm length pin.

Footprint is pinheader(male) but expected component is pinsocket(female)
Cut the component to 16 pins or use similar one it has around 10mm length pin.
Please use modules that have telec mark.
